{"tid":474551,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一個國家廢到點先允許自己地方既人係講緊幾種語言","createTime":"2017-11-20T09:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T05:07:03.000Z","uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"177bc4d455acf4684157c9aad7b38a19c0a7a6d1","tid":474551,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"而又唔知對方講緊乜<br />\n<br />\n東南西北文化又唔同宗教又唔同個種又唔同，都叫一個國家？<br />\n<br />\n然後要不停東拉西扯，將d人拉埋一齊做交流<br />\n<br />\n將d人拉埋一齊果d人叫官，而個個官既屋企人都唔係呢個國家既人黎<br />\n<br />\n去曬做外國人，學外國既文化，講外國既語言<br />\n<br />\n自己都唔鐘意呢個地方，又要人係呢個地方住得好開心，唔準講呢個地方既衰野<br />\n<br />\n乜野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1e6d359354dbba4964dd6aa78ab5a25c9b45da","tid":474551,"uid":53660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"比利時？<br />\n<br />\n瑞士？<br />\n<br />\n西班牙？"},{"pid":"cae9834522f9722c3106b033f12cfb4e0f77a02e","tid":474551,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:40:57.000Z","msg":"我估佢講緊鄰國地獄鬼國?"},{"pid":"deadb4651fc433dbc1ef4a31415f4f8e85ac5beb","tid":474551,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"唔係想阻你反共, 就我所知 加拿大 (英/法語), 瑞士 (德/法/意大利語), 比利時 (荷/德/法語)"},{"pid":"5eb26390bd10ddf683292c8085127f017f5194d9","tid":474551,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b1c9849d51e5f25570f4a6cbc61732cd47e6c9e","tid":474551,"uid":80176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"中國"},{"pid":"d3cecc8edcba47b56b53fa0d3bcbfee2b10d637b","tid":474551,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"美國"},{"pid":"9903f0e3815550a22e0c519cfc84cdb90513208d","tid":474551,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"Canada"}]}